channel.title: Simple help, how to add custom items onto 317 PI insidiax
channel.description:
hey guys, please help me , i want to add custom items, custom phats, custom santa's and custom wepons, but i dont know where to add them , can anyone help me and tell me where to add them or put the codes in, ? and it would be wonderful if you could also provide the some codes for custom items,
thanks

item.title: Simple help, how to add custom items onto 317 PI insidiax
item.dc:creator: @malimt malimt
item.description:
@malimt wrote:

sk8rdude461:

90% is done client sided. Start by adding the models (if it’s phats or such, there are no models), then add the ints to itemdef.java

can you explain more on how to add the customs , because this is my first time and i really dont know how to add it properly and idk what the codes are for them :S
